BJhwQ0EeJx.description: Shift bits count. Truncated to an integer. Negative values round to zero
BJhwQ0EeJx.label: N

@/debounce-true.description: Debounces a boolean value. The `OUT` value would change only after a period of at least `Ts` seconds while which the input state `ST` has not changed. The node is useful to fight signal bouncing of mechanical switches.

S1ei06X9g1x.description: Resets current countdown, i.e. cancels the delay
S1ei06X9g1x.label: RST

BkWjR67qx1x.description: Outputs true when delay is in progress
BkWjR67qx1x.label: ACT

HyXiAam9gkx.description: Resets current countdown, starts new countdown
HyXiAam9gkx.label: SET
